The Lakes District Technocity(established in 2004) is a science park located on the campus of SÃ¼leyman Demirel University. The technocity is a full member of International Association of Science Parks. The science park occupies 112000 squaremeters area.
The activities of the technocity include Energy and Renewable Energy, Internet Technology and Services / E-Business, Plasma Technology, and Environment Technologies.
